line_1: To what lov'd haunt you whilom did erect;
line_2: Trim Maenelaus, with piny verdure deck'd.
Or dost Thou, weary grown, these Works neglect,

line_1: NYMPHS! o'er the soil ten thousand points erect,
line_2: And high in air the electric flame collect.
Delights us, by engaging our respect.
And make my Muse the Architect;

line_1: Let Europe sav'd the Column high erect,
line_2: Where sembling Art may carve the fair Effect,
To form a more voluptuous sect;

line_1: Tho' on thy Grave no Statue I erect,
line_2: Yet the smooth Stone shall with my Tears be deck'd.
